'''比爾·斯蒂爾'''（{{lang-en|William T. "Bill" Still}}，{{bd|1948年|1月20日||}}）是[[美國|美國]][[紀錄片|紀錄片]]製片人和作家，代表作為《金钱主人》和《奧茲的秘密》。

== 生平 ==
斯蒂爾執導過《金钱主人》（1996年）和《奧茲的秘密》（2009年）等批判[[美聯儲|美聯儲]]貨幣控制系統的紀錄片<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.vueweekly.com/front/story/cash_of_the_titans|title=Cash of the titans|date=2004-08-25|work=Vue Weekly|accessdate=2021-01-26|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406081917/http://www.vueweekly.com/front/story/cash_of_the_titans/|archivedate=2012-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Documentary exposes massive Federal Reserve fraud|url=https://www.wnd.com/2008/06/42574/|accessdate=2021-01-25|date=2008-06-13|publisher=WorldNetDaily|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130201122/https://www.wnd.com/2008/06/42574/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中《奧茲的秘密》在2010年{{le|貝洛伊特國際電影節|Beloit International Film Festival}}上獲得最佳紀錄片獎<ref>{{Cite web|title=2010 BIFFY Awards|url=http://www.beloitfilmfest.org/2010-award-finalists-biffy-winners|accessdate=2021-01-26|publisher=Beloit International Film Festival|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801135154/http://www.beloitfilmfest.org/2010-award-finalists-biffy-winners/|archivedate=2012-08-01}}</ref>。

2011年10月，斯蒂爾宣布角逐[[自由意志黨|自由意志黨]]的總統競選提名<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://maxkeiser.com/2011/10/11/bill-still-seeks-libertarian-nomination-for-president-nationalize-the-currency-not-the-banks|title=Bill Still Seeks Libertarian Nomination for President: “Nationalize the Currency, Not the Banks”|date=2011-10-11|work=MaxKeiser.com|accessdate=2021-01-26|language=en|archivedate=2013-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130315120935/http://maxkeiser.com/2011/10/11/bill-still-seeks-libertarian-nomination-for-president-nationalize-the-currency-not-the-banks}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bill Still Announces Run for Libertarian Party Presidential Nomination|url=https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2011/10/bill-still-announces-run-for-libertarian-party-presidential-nomination/|accessdate=2021-01-25|publisher=Independent Political Report|date=2011-10|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130162315/https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2011/10/bill-still-announces-run-for-libertarian-party-presidential-nomination/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bill Still’s “Address to the Libertarian Nation” Contains New Proposals, Disagreements with LP Positions|url=https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2011/12/lp-pres-bill-stills-address-to-the-libertarian-nation-contains-new-proposals-disagreements-with-lp-positions/|accessdate=2021-01-25|publisher=Independent Political Report|date=2011-12|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201222113/https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2011/12/lp-pres-bill-stills-address-to-the-libertarian-nation-contains-new-proposals-disagreements-with-lp-positions/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但在2012年{{link-en|自由意志黨全國代表大會|Libertarian National Convention}}上最終由[[蓋瑞·強生|蓋瑞·強生]]贏得提名。

== 作品 ==

* 1996年，《金钱主人》（''The Money Masters''）
* 2009年，《奧茲的秘密》（''The Secret of Oz''）
* 2010年，《奧茲的秘密2》（''Secret of Oz 2''）
* 2013年，《哲基爾島：美聯儲背後的真相》（''Jekyll Island, The Truth Behind The Federal Reserve''）<ref>{{Cite web|title='Jekyll Island' film shocker – $4.95 today only!|url=https://www.wnd.com/2013/10/jekyll-island-film-documentary-4-95-today-only/|accessdate=2021-01-25|date=2013-10-29|publisher=WorldNetDaily|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130052002/https://www.wnd.com/2013/10/jekyll-island-film-documentary-4-95-today-only/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
作家{{link-en|G·愛德華·格里芬|G. Edward Griffin}}認為斯蒂爾的紀錄片是出色的作品，但提供了錯誤的解決方案<ref>{{Cite web|title=MEET BILL STILL, FIAT-MONEY ADVOCATE|url=http://www.freedomforceinternational.org/freedomcontent.cfm?fuseaction=meetstill|accessdate=2021-01-26|last=Griffin|first=G. Edward|publisher=Freedom Force International|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516015243/http://www.freedomforceinternational.org/freedomcontent.cfm?fuseaction=meetstill|archivedate=2012-05-16}}</ref>。調查記者和作家[[諾米·普林斯|諾米·普林斯]]在2009年評論說，《金钱主人》「出色地揭示了美聯儲和強大的全球金融家背後的真相」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Three Documentaries on the Federal Reserve|url=http://www.cineaste.com/articles/three-documentaries-on-the-federal-reserve|accessdate=2021-01-26|author=|date=|last=Prins|first=Nomi|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121216095923/http://www.cineaste.com/articles/three-documentaries-on-the-federal-reserve|archivedate=2012-12-16|quote=The Money Masters, is simply outstanding. Directed and narrated by Bill Still, it does a superb job of revealing the truth behind the Fed and the powerful global financiers whose self-interest has dictated our banking system from the beginning.}}</ref>。

